summary: Relating to Land Use and Zoning; amending Plat 55W, Page 138 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone property located at 3021 S.W. Bradford Street from General Commercial (CG) and portion of Single-Family Residential (SF 5000) to Multi-family residential (Low rise 3) Zone and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith (Petition of Keith Putnam, Agent for R.D.
